-Hi.

46:33.949 --> 46:35.784
So, this tableau...

46:35.868 --> 46:38.037
-Yeah, please. Please go in.
-Katrina?

46:38.120 --> 46:39.580
I've seen it.

46:47.423 --> 46:50.259
-Fergal came round last night.
-I know.

46:50.342 --> 46:53.221
I can't believe you made up
all those stories about us.

46:53.305 --> 46:55.891
What stories?

46:55.974 --> 46:59.562
-Maybe he got
the wrong end of the stick.
-Yeah, right.

46:59.645 --> 47:01.522
I just told him we were
friends, that's all.

47:01.606 --> 47:04.234
Well, then you
lied 'cause we're not.

47:04.318 --> 47:06.487
Well,
what did you want me to say?

47:06.570 --> 47:11.576
I think I've seen enough.
Frankly,
Mr MacDonald, I'm surprised.

47:11.659 --> 47:15.330
I was expecting a tableau
of life in a stately home.

47:15.413 --> 47:18.292
-Yeah, I'm sorry.
We had a bit of...
-But this...

47:18.376 --> 47:23.340
This has real texture,
real atmosphere.

47:23.423 --> 47:26.301
-I mean, you can smell it.
-It does stink a bit.

47:26.385 --> 47:32.392
Oh, no. It just makes
the whole thing so intense.

47:32.475 --> 47:35.813
If it was up to me, I'd
authorise a grant right now.

47:35.896 --> 47:38.732
Oh, that's great!

47:38.816 --> 47:40.610
What do you mean,
if it was up to you?

47:40.693 --> 47:44.364
Katrina's the other
delegate so it's her call.

47:44.447 --> 47:46.325
So, what do you think?

47:47.868 --> 47:49.537
What do I think?

47:51.247 --> 47:53.917
I think it's not just clever,
it's cunning.

47:54.000 --> 47:56.962
It'd fool anyone.
It certainly fooled me.

47:59.674 --> 48:04.054
There you go, Mr MacDonald.
That's what you
wanted to hear, isn't it?

